Sit down with some of the FedEx team

Sit down with some of the FedEx team

From drivers to analysts, hundreds of thousands of global team members work for you. Too bad you can’t meet
every one! But here’s a chance to get to know us a little better.

From drivers to analysts, hundreds of thousands of global team members work for you. Too bad you can’t meet every one! But here’s a chance to get to know us a little better.

(Left to right) Patrick Blanar, international sales executive; Ashley Carpenter, field sales executive; Doug Carpenter, pilot; Kristen Dennington, customer success executive, and Brittany Minin, customer success executive

For Doug Carpenter, his three daughters, and his son-in-law, FedEx and family go hand in hand

“FedEx means a great deal to my family,” said Brittany. “My sisters and I always loved watching my dad’s planes take off.”

Sure, being a FedEx pilot for many years is rewarding, but for Doug: “My three proudest moments at FedEx happened when my daughters were hired.”

And everyone’s future at FedEx is looking bright. “The future excites me because of the company’s relentless pursuit of innovation and its focus on cutting-edge technology,” said Kristen. “I love being part of a company that continually evolves to meet the challenges of tomorrow.”

Using core values to create smarter supply chains

Flexibility, efficiency, and intelligence are at the heart of our efforts.

Flexibility

  • Offering a simplified delivery experience for customers with the unified FedEx Network 2.0.
  • Helping businesses streamline operations with logistics services, automation,
    and supply chain visibility

Flexibility

  • Offering a simplified delivery experience for customers with the unified FedEx Network 2.0.
  • Helping businesses streamline operations with logistics services, automation, and supply chain visibility

Efficiency

  • Improving how we pick up, transport, and deliver packages with Network 2.0
  • Focusing on sustainability initiatives like reducing emissions, and enabling
    businesses to track their carbon footprints
  • Consistently meeting customer and regulatory requirements—we have a global ISO 9001 certification

Efficiency

  • Focusing on sustainability initiatives like reducing emissions, and enabling businesses to track their carbon footprints
  • Consistently meeting customer and regulatory requirements—we have a global ISO 9001 certification

Intelligence

  • Delivering data-driven insights to empower businesses to make decisions
  • Using our Quality Driven Management principles to take innovative ideas from
    concept to launch
